GCFPCA 0.0.0.9000
  • Reference
  • Articles
  • GitHub
A method for performing generalized conditional functional principal components analysis. The method allows the outcome Y to follow exponential family distributions, including binomial and Poisson, accommodating FPCA of binary and count data.
